{"tid":1662734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋係唔係都應該Stand With Catalonia?","createTime":"2019-10-19T03:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T06:44:43.000Z","uid":129134,"like":58,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"32eef49e2283889f5a00695f6bcab5339c675085","tid":1662734,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"加泰警察射盲左3個人隻眼<br />\n學香港狗隻由天台射催淚彈<br />\n瘋狂拉記者<br />\n周圍打人扑頭<br />\n同香港一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港搵國際幫手咁多次<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋都要比支持同病相憐嘅城市</span></span></strong><br />\n亦要令共匪睇到：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">全世界都望住香港！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊嘅遊行<br />\n比全世界睇到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">HONG KONG STANDS WITH CATALONIA!!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e04e543610cec194469d9ee84fcc4042ec77a0d0","tid":1662734,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"推！1/10"},{"pid":"177a7736fe5c13e805e08a0ab33d2c01f5fd349f","tid":1662734,"uid":177554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:14:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8344b6fc946e496bd1d9ba072e7cd27135b6365","tid":1662734,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290d21058a6c4a79542877f84a0cb7dae0f7af15","tid":1662734,"uid":23169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:19:10.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid